      <scopecontent>
         <head>Scope and Content Information</head>
         <p>Correspondence concerning personnel actions including
         letters of appointment, re-appointment, promotions, title
         changes, special salary actions, and resignations for the
         University and Clinch Valley College.</p>
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement>
         <head>Organization/Arrangement</head>
         <p>Box 1: Personnel actions, Clinch Valley College, elections,
         re-elections, promotions, leave of absences, resignations,
         appointments 1972-1974, Personnel actions, appointments and
         re-appointments 1975 October 3- 1976 May 28, Personnel actions
         changes of title 1975 Oct 3-1976 May 28, Personnel actions,
         elections 1975 Oct 3, Personnel actions elections 1976 Jan 23,
         Personnel actions elections 1976 Mar 26, Personnel actions
         elections 1976 May 28, Personnel actions leaves of absences
         1976 May 28.</p>
         <p>Box 2: Personnel actions, promotions 1975-1976, Personnel
         actions re-elections 1975-Oct 3, 1976 Jan 23, Personnel
         actions, re-elections change of re-election re-appointments
         1976 Mar 26, May 28, Personnel actions resignations 1975-1976,
         Personnel actions special salary actions 1975 Oct 3.</p>
      </arrangement>
